Bootstrap 4 - dev notes from brad traversy

jQuery is required


CLASSES
container - kind of centers
page-header - for h[1-7]
lead - for paragraphs


TAGS
small, mark, del, u

CONTEXTUAL COLORS
primary, success, warning, info, danger

ALIGNMENT & Transformation
text-[left,right,center,justify,nowrap]
text-[lowercase,uppercase,capitalize]

QUICK FLOATS
pull-[right,left,center]

CLEAR FIX - clear when you use float
clearfix

Some Tags
blockquote, blockquote-reverse
cite:title
code, kbd

LIST
list-unstyle - to remove the bullets (the style)
list-inline


CONTEXTUAL COLORS
[bg,text]-[primary, success, warning, info, danger, muted]

BUTTON
btn - format as a button
colors -> btn-[default, primary, success, warning, info, danger, link]
sizes -> btn-[lg, sm, xs]
btn[disabled=disabled]
add role="button" to link to make it behave as a button


FORMS
<div class="container">
	<form>
		<div class="form-group">
			<label>Name</label>
			<input type="text" class="form-control" />
		</div>
	</form>
</div>

give form[class=form-inlinie] for an inline form

TABLE
table[class=table]
table-[striped, bordered, hover, condensed]
tr[class=primary, success, warning, info, danger]

47:04
LIST
[ul,ol][class=list-group]
li[class=list-group-item

PANELS
panel
panel-default
panel-deading
panel-title
panel-body
panel-footer

WELLS
well
well-[lg, sm]

ALERT
alert
alert-[primary, success, warning, info, danger]
add role="alert"
alert-dismissable - to close an alert
<div class="alert alert-warning alert-dismissable">
	<button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert">
		<span>&times;</span>
	</button> you can close this alert
</div>


PROGRESS BAR
<div class="progress">
	<div class="progress-bar" style="width:50%;">
	50%
	</div>
</div>

add contextual class
progress-bar-[primary, success, warning, info, danger], striped, active to animate

LABELS
label label-[primary, success, warning, info, danger]

BADGES
<a href="#">Inbox <span class="badge">2</span></a>


IMAGES
thumbnail, img-[circle, rounded]

GRID
grids have 12 blocks
row>col








